Cecilia Loftus https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cecilia_Loftus 0 Cecilia Loftus (born Marie Cecilia Loftus Brown, 22 October 1876 – 12 July 1943) was a Scottish actress, singer, mimic, vaudevillian, and music hall performer in the late 19th and early 20th centuries.
